title: Tiger Woods Is A McRib
description: Katie and Ashley answer a voicemail about Ninja not streaming with women (:15), the most important news from the NFL preseason including Tyrod Taylor's name pronunciation, Cam vs Kelvin, Jalen Ramsey's suspension, Antonio Callaway's punishment and Deflategate II (13:30), is Tiger Woods really back or is he just back for a limited time (28:00), coaches doing weird stuff (32:00), with no more Bachelorette, Ashley discusses a social media Top-3 post (35:00), Bake Your Take on "Aspirational Packing" (46:00) and a final voicemail about what to do with foul balls at a baseball game (55:00).
